{"tid":97370,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"細個同大個對哈利波特不同既睇法","createTime":"2017-01-27T15:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T05:43:35.000Z","uid":861,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e9c6565607148004d2e09263fe99eb097c7e273f","tid":97370,"uid":861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:05:10.000Z","msg":"最近重睇返 由第一部睇到去第六部 <br />\n第7同第8仲未睇<br />\n以前細個覺得頭四集好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好新奇 魔法好正 又有鬼魂 山怪人等元素 而第456集都覺得好悶 睇到訓著 所以一直都未睇第7同8 <br />\n但而家睇返 反而覺得頭三集好悶 拍攝同劇情都好一般 有少少低b既感覺<br />\n第4集仲係覺得咁好睇 最後黑魔王復活一直都好深刻好震撼<br />\n而第5集拍攝進步左好多 d色調同前四集唔同 鄧不利多同黑魔王對戰終於唔係淨係光線對撞 會玩下水 火 風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第6集雖然文戲多 但最後鄧不利多死真係好撚震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n聽日睇埋第7第8集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2fa1561408a40a88b103dadbf66461b0d4a6d0","tid":97370,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:06:55.000Z","msg":"以前睇覺得靚就得<br />\n<br />\n而家人大咗 , 就知道 原來身材都好重要"},{"pid":"eab1646b38886b80a096c1b5bcb0e42afbf3b7e0","tid":97370,"uid":1773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:24:32.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦，肯定係第三集拍得最好 無論storytelling定technical"},{"pid":"818959dec0b4001dac39221a2819af3ae4fad41e","tid":97370,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:34:30.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺哈利一開始就係衛斯里面前<br />\n借買零食為由 show自己d身家<br />\n好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8cdbc6c36acf0b0041071a43291f87ff215d83","tid":97370,"uid":861,"l